  "relevance": {
    "_comment": "Edit these lists anytime — no code changes needed. Keywords match whole words/phrases (case-insensitive) against listing name + industry + description. Empty include list = all industries pass. States are 2-letter codes; empty include_states = national. priority_states listings get flagged/starred, never filtered. Size bounds: null = no bound. unknown_cash_flow_min_asking_price: listings that don't disclose cash flow are kept only if asking price is at least this (proxy for the $300K SDE floor).",
